t: "There is no blame on you for subtly showing interest in ňĻdivorced or widowedňļ women¬†or for hiding ňĻthe intentionňļ in your hearts. Allah knows that you are considering them ňĻfor marriageňļ. But do not make a secret commitment with them‚ÄĒyou can only show interest in them appropriately. Do not commit to the bond of marriage until the waiting period expires. Know that Allah is aware of what is in your hearts, so beware of Him. And know that Allah is All-Forgiving, Most Forbearing"